OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cahead of evidence in 'sexual offences'
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FFormer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson has arrived at court ahead
OL,9,Fof the first evidence being heard in
OL,10,Fhis trial over alleged historical
OL,11,Fsexual offences.
OL,13,FIt is expected that the first witness
OL,14,Fin the case, Complainant A, will be
OL,15,Fcalled to give evidence on Thursday at
OL,16,FNewry Crown Court.
OL,18,FThe former MP is accused of rape and
OL,19,Fseveral counts of gross indecency and
OL,20,Fof indecent assault.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
