OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779984666
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cahead of evidence in 'sexual offences'
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FDonaldson, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,8,Fto the 18 alleged offences.
OL,10,FThe charges span a time period between
OL,11,F1985 and 2008 involving two alleged
OL,12,Fvictims.
OL,14,FDonaldson's wife Lady Eleanor
OL,15,FDonaldson denies several charges of
OL,16,Faiding and abetting her husband's
OL,17,Falleged offending.
OL,19,FShe is facing a trial of the facts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
