OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779984666
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson arrives at court
OL,4,Cahead of evidence in 'sexual offences'
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, prosecuting barrister
OL,8,FRosemary Walsh KC delivered her
OL,9,Fopening statement and said two women
OL,10,Fclaim the former MP subjected them to
OL,11,F"difficult and traumatic incidents"
OL,12,Fwhen they were children.
OL,14,FA police interview with Complainant A
OL,15,Fis expected to be played to the jury
OL,16,Fon Thursday before she is cross-
OL,17,Fexamined.
